# Affiliate Analytics & Project Management Walkthrough

This update introduces a comprehensive system for managing affiliate projects, separating AI-generated leads from official projects, and tracking ROI through manual data entry integrated with Ads data.

## Key Features

### 1. Project Categorization
Projects are now divided into two tabs in the **Quản lý dự án** page:
- **Dự án chính thức**: Projects you are actively running and tracking.
- **Dự án từ AI Agents**: Leads saved from search results that need review.

### 2. Manual Affiliate Tracking
For official projects, a new **Phân tích ROAS & CVR** tab is available in the detail page. This allows you to:
- **Link Ads Campaigns**: Select which Google/Facebook ads are driving traffic to this project.
- **Manual Data Entry**: Enter daily results (RefCount, Conversions, Revenue) directly from your affiliate program dashboard.
- **ROI Visualization**: View real-time ROAS and CVR charts that combine your actual Ads Spend with your manual Revenue data.

### 3. Workflow Automation
- **Promote to Official**: Easily move an AI Agent lead to the official list with one click.
- **Persistent Storage**: All data is saved locally for immediate use without backend overhead.

## Screenshots & Demos

> [!TIP]
